              </li>
              <li permid="CSU">
                <m>S</m> has an identity with respect to <m>\ast</m>, but the identity is not <m>A</m>.
              </li>
              <li permid="jad">
                <m>S</m> has an identity, but not every element has an inverse under <m>\ast</m>.
              </li>
              <li permid="Phm">
                <m>\ast</m> is commutative, <m>S</m> has an identity, and every element has an inverse under <m>\ast</m>.
